responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "2D764DEF44A99DB300030F835103518B", "We\'re grateful for the help.  The bandits have been getting more organized and aggressively taking territory to the south of Lionhold and now hold Lumber Landing.  Our scouts have spotted a command camp up on the bluffs to the southwest.  We need someone to get up there and disrupt their command structure.  Without orders, the bandits should be easier for us to push off the river.")
name: DD_SQ_0009_SergeantVenalis_4_Response
